<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA512_02_SU_0004_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_01.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_02.css" />

  <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema512_02_0004.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema512_02_su_0004" data-current-page="page_3">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="2_green" lang="y">나눗셈식을 이용하여 6을 나누어떨어지게 하는 수를 알아봅시다.</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="input_area">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">나눗셈식을 완성해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="page_1_cover">
            <div class="input_area">
              <div class="question_box flex align_center">
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span>6&divide;1=6</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span>6&divide;2=</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span>6&divide;3=2</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              <div class="question_box flex align_center">
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span>6&divide;4=1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span class="text-vertical">&hellip;</span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_8">
                  <span>6&divide;5=1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-vertical">&hellip;</span></span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span>6&divide;6=</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer3">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">6을 나누어떨어지게 하는 수를 모두 써 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="question_box">
              <div class="flex gap_12">
                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap_12">
                <span>,</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap_12">
                <span>,</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap_12">
                <span>,</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      <article class="page page_3">
        <div class="summarize_wrap">
          <div class="summarize">
            <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>

            <div>
              <span lang="y">6을 나누어떨어지게 하는 수인 1, 2, 3, 6을 </span>
              <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="6의 약수" lang="y" onclick="countClick(this)">6의 약수</button>
              <span lang="y" class="small-gap">라고 합니다.</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span lang="y">이와 같이 어떤 수를 나누어떨어지게 하는 수를</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span lang="y">그 수의</span>
              <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="약수" lang="y" onclick="countClick(this)">약수</button>
              <span lang="y" class="small-gap">라고 합니다.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="etc_img" >
              <p lang="y">어떤 수의 약수에는 1과 자기 자신이 항상 포함돼요.</p>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA512_02_SU/0009_contents_2.png"
                alt="어떤 수의 약수에는 1과 자기자신이 항상 포함돼요. 라고 말하는 선생님 그림" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset" lang="y">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck" lang="y">확인</button>
        <button class="btnCheck etcImgOn" lang="y" onclick="countClick(this)">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>